title: 03/15/22 DPS Best Of

description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Mike Florio about Tom Brady's decision to return from retirement. IS he ready to pay off on a bet with Paulie ? Peter King checks in about some of the QBs that have been moved this off season. And Todd discovers he has an issue with pronouncing S's.
